Parsek
--------------------

Parsek is a KDE 4 client for playing multi-player turn-based strategy games
set in space which are built using Thousand Parsec framework.

These games are known as 4X games, from the main phases found in them: eXplore,
eXpand, eXploit and eXterminate. Some examples of games which Parsek and 
Thousand Parsec draw ideas from are Stars!, VGA Planets, Master of Orion and 
Galactic Civilizations.

